resources.description: The map includes estimates for the demand of beneficial energy for heating of buildings and hot water for use (expressed in MJ) in the level municipalities.The primary data on these calculations, emanate from the inventory of residences and population in 2001, as they are published by the National Statistical Authority. The statistical calculations are indicative provided that they depend from the adoption of big number of parameters.
resources.name: Demand of energy for heating by households
